<h2 class="bold font-l">"I want to be perfect!"</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
A ghost uses Janine's desire to be prettier to drive her off the deep end. </p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="alt-titles section section-fact">
<h3>
<strong>Alternative Title(s):</strong>
<span>Vain</span>, <span>Being Ugly Sucks</span> </h3>
